<Defs>
  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseRamboGun">
    <defName>Gun_Tec-9_RWP</defName>
    <label>Tec-9</label>
    <description>The Tec-9 is a compact submachine gun notable for its high rate of fire, making it effective in close-quarters combat. Though less accurate than its larger counterparts, it compensates with rapid bursts of bullets, overwhelming targets with sheer volume. Easy to manufacture and maintain, it's a popular choice among improvised militias and raider gangs.</description>
